## Phase 5 — SVG & Inline Style Fixes

Some SVG elements (radar chart, gauge arcs) use hardcoded `rgba(255,255,255,...)` in JSX. These need a conditional:

```jsx
// At top of component:
import { useTheme } from './ThemeProvider.jsx';
const { theme } = useTheme();

// Usage:
const gridColor = theme === 'light' ? 'rgba(0,0,0,0.08)' : 'rgba(255,255,255,0.05)';
const axisColor = theme === 'light' ? 'rgba(0,0,0,0.06)' : 'rgba(255,255,255,0.05)';
```

Components affected:
- **OverviewPage.jsx** — radar chart grid lines & gauge arc background
- **App.jsx** — any inline style references

---

## Execution Order (Safe Rollout)

| Step | What | Risk |
|------|------|------|
| 1 | Add CSS light variables to [index.css](file:///home/aarush_linux/projects/PBL/frontend/src/index.css) | ✅ Zero — additive only, no selector touches existing code |
| 2 | Create `ThemeProvider.jsx` | ✅ Zero — new file |
| 3 | Wrap App in `ThemeProvider` in [main.jsx](file:///home/aarush_linux/projects/PBL/frontend/src/main.jsx) | ✅ Near-zero — one-line wrapper, defaults to `dark` |
| 4 | Add toggle button to [Sidebar.jsx](file:///home/aarush_linux/projects/PBL/frontend/src/components/Sidebar.jsx) | ✅ Low — new button, no existing UI changes |
| 5 | Migrate Tailwind classes in components (one by one) | ⚠️ Medium — visual regressions possible, test each |
| 6 | Fix inline SVG colors in [OverviewPage.jsx](file:///home/aarush_linux/projects/PBL/frontend/src/components/OverviewPage.jsx) | ⚠️ Medium — visual only |
| 7 | Update [App.css](file:///home/aarush_linux/projects/PBL/frontend/src/App.css) selection color | ✅ Zero |

> [!TIP]
> **Steps 1–4 can ship independently** — they add the toggle but the dark theme still looks exactly the same because the semantic utilities aren't swapped yet. This gives you a safe checkpoint.

